  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43211839_7_4064-4242",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "4064-4242",
      "markText": "还有，平素不大交往的人，忽而寄给我一个红帖子，上面印着“为舍妹出阁”，“小儿完姻”，“敬请观礼”或“阖第光临”这些含有“阴险的暗示”[18]的句子，使我不化钱便总觉得有些过意不去的，我也不十分高兴。",
      "totalCount": 390,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43211839&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=4064&rangeEnd=4242",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b1e32ea072935c3fb1eecd3?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=4064&rangeEnd=4242"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43211839_8_5591-5612",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "5591-5612",
      "markText": "仁厚黑暗的地母呵，愿在你怀里永安她的魂灵！",
      "totalCount": 192,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43211839&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=5591&rangeEnd=5612",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b1e32ea072935c3fb1eecd3?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=5591&rangeEnd=5612"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43211839_7_2131-2304",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "2131-2304",
      "markText": "虫蛆也许是不干净的，但它们并没有自鸣清高；鸷禽猛兽以较弱的动物为饵，不妨说是凶残的罢，但它们从来就没有竖过“公理”“正义”[10]的旗子，使牺牲者直到被吃的时候为止，还是一味佩服赞叹它们。",
      "totalCount": 180,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43211839&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2131&rangeEnd=2304",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b1e32ea072935c3fb1eecd3?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2131&rangeEnd=2304"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43211839_10_4712-4739",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "4712-4739",
      "markText": "我至今一想起，还诧异我的父亲何以要在那时候叫我来背书。",
      "totalCount": 168,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43211839&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=4712&rangeEnd=4739",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b1e32ea072935c3fb1eecd3?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=4712&rangeEnd=4739"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43211839_6_1302-1381",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1302-1381",
      "markText": "凡这些，都是极其鲜美可口的；都曾是使我思乡的蛊惑。后来，我在久别之后尝到了，也不过如此；惟独在记忆上，还有旧来的意味留存。他们也许要哄骗我一生，使我时时反顾。",
      "totalCount": 165,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43211839&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1302&rangeEnd=1381",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b1e32ea072935c3fb1eecd3?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1302&rangeEnd=1381"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43211839_12_1459-1489",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "1459-1489",
      "markText": "结末的教训是：所以倘有陌生的声音叫你的名字，你万不可答应他。",
      "totalCount": 156,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43211839&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=1459&rangeEnd=1489",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b1e32ea072935c3fb1eecd3?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=1459&rangeEnd=1489"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43211839_8_4462-4483",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "4462-4483",
      "markText": "哥儿，有画儿的‘三哼经’，我给你买来了！”",
      "totalCount": 132,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43211839&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=4462&rangeEnd=4483",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b1e32ea072935c3fb1eecd3?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=4462&rangeEnd=4483"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43211839_13_5191-5279",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "5191-5279",
      "markText": "“父亲！！！”我还叫他，一直到他咽了气。 我现在还听到那时的自己的这声音，每听到时，就觉得这却是我对于父亲的最大的错处。",
      "totalCount": 128,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43211839&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=5191&rangeEnd=5279",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b1e32ea072935c3fb1eecd3?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=5191&rangeEnd=5279"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43211839_7_2543-2695",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "2543-2695",
      "markText": "正如我们在万生园[12]里，看见猴子翻筋斗，母象请安，虽然往往破颜一笑，但同时也觉得不舒服，甚至于感到悲哀，以为这些多余的聪明，倒不如没有的好罢。",
      "totalCount": 126,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43211839&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2543&rangeEnd=2695",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b1e32ea072935c3fb1eecd3?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2543&rangeEnd=2695"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43211839_7_7770-7824",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "7770-7824",
      "markText": "中国的官兵就常在实做的，他们总不肯扫清土匪或扑灭敌人，因为这么一来，就要不被重视，甚至于因失其用处而被裁汰。",
      "totalCount": 126,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43211839&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=7770&rangeEnd=7824",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b1e32ea072935c3fb1eecd3?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=7770&rangeEnd=7824"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43211839_6_535-574",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "535-574",
      "markText": "一个人做到只剩了回忆的时候，生涯大概总要算是无聊了罢，但有时竟会连回忆也没有。",
      "totalCount": 121,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43211839&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=535&rangeEnd=574",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b1e32ea072935c3fb1eecd3?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=535&rangeEnd=574"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43211839_9_6562-6591",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "6562-6591",
      "markText": "然而我已经不但自己不敢再想做孝子，并且怕我父亲去做孝子了。",
      "totalCount": 121,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43211839&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=6562&rangeEnd=6591",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b1e32ea072935c3fb1eecd3?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=6562&rangeEnd=6591"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43211839_9_511-604",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "511-604",
      "markText": "我总要上下四方寻求，得到一种最黑，最黑，最黑的咒文，先来诅咒一切反对白话，妨害白话者。即使人死了真有灵魂，因这最恶的心，应该堕入地狱，也将决不改悔，总要先来诅咒一切反对白话，妨害白话者。",
      "totalCount": 119,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43211839&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=511&rangeEnd=604",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b1e32ea072935c3fb1eecd3?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=511&rangeEnd=604"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43211839_16_2145-2221",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "2145-2221",
      "markText": "从此我总觉得这范爱农离奇，而且很可恶。天下可恶的人，当初以为是满人，这时才知道还在其次；第一倒是范爱农。中国不革命则已，要革命，首先就必须将范爱农除去。",
      "totalCount": 119,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43211839&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=2145&rangeEnd=2221",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b1e32ea072935c3fb1eecd3?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=2145&rangeEnd=2221"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43211839_7_5860-5896",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "5860-5896",
      "markText": "现在是粗俗了，在路上遇见人类的迎娶仪仗，也不过当作性交的广告看，不甚留心",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43211839&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=5860&rangeEnd=5896",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b1e32ea072935c3fb1eecd3?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=5860&rangeEnd=5896"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43211839_15_4579-4624",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "4579-4624",
      "markText": "中国是弱国，所以中国人当然是低能儿，分数在六十分以上，便不是自己的能力了：也无怪他们疑惑。",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43211839&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=4579&rangeEnd=4624",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b1e32ea072935c3fb1eecd3?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=4579&rangeEnd=4624"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43211839_12_707-784",
